{"tid":2112305,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大新聞系總監向師生發信 籲無懼「紅線」捍衛真相","createTime":"2020-07-17T08:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T11:48:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":493,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"8d0a0fda94d86f436302fb6c47a14e2b5a84c76c","tid":2112305,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200717/4ALWYPQZMDBVT5HTVBJ4D2MH7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2F4ALWYPQZMDBVT5HTVBJ4D2MH7Q%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpW1VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=d8b8a25e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2F4ALWYPQZMDBVT5HTVBJ4D2MH7Q%2F&h=ca4470ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200717/4ALWYPQZMDBVT5HTVBJ4D2MH7Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n「港區國安法」生效，本港新聞自由危在旦夕。香港大學新聞及傳媒研究中心今發電郵給師生，總監瑞凱德（Keith Richburg）直言《國安法》影響新聞和學術自由，亦為教學帶來挑戰，甚至有人問「新聞專業還有沒有未來？」他在信中回應，新聞界的未來取決於前線記者會否畏縮、向權勢折腰，在腦海中設置「紅線」，屈服於自我檢查的誘惑。他認為，本港採訪環境將會變得如內地一樣，但港大不打算教導學生退縮，下一代記者應學習，如何繞過無形且不斷變化的「紅線」，以難以反駁的事實和報道來檢驗界限，繼續向政權說真相。"},{"pid":"5f6549d6657f86780ed60ff8bd36fd450f56e85d","tid":2112305,"uid":271497,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:13:52.000Z","msg":"Respect<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7c2c1f0984bc7e94ae5bf98b6cec6100f1ff15","tid":2112305,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f6549d6657f86780ed60ff8bd36fd450f56e85d","tid":2112305,"uid":271497,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:13:52.000Z","msg":"Respect<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 